{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777267168878,"sessionID":"ses_2329f5659ffeTumX9K8lxuV4OV","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_jaXhAZ7WUohYVnTD1eIB6YLH","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report\\runbook.md","limit":2000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report\\runbook.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # GitHub 热点仓库长期摘取整理报告 Runbook\n2: \n3: ## 1. 目的\n4: \n5: 本 runbook 用于指导后续 agent 或人工在**不使用 GitHub token、密钥、登录态**的前提下，持续产出 GitHub 热点仓库 Markdown 报告。\n6: \n7: ## 2. 运行前提\n8: \n9: - 目标目录：`D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report`\n10: - 数据来源必须是公开、无需认证的页面或接口。\n11: - 不依赖外部服务部署。\n12: - 如无法联网，可退回人工占位/样例维护，但必须如实标注。\n13: \n14: ## 3. 手动运行步骤\n15: \n16: ### 方案 A：纯人工整理\n17: \n18: 1. 打开 GitHub Trending 页面或其他公开热点来源。\n19: 2. 记录本期观察日期、来源、时间范围（如 daily / weekly）。\n20: 3. 选取若干热点仓库，整理以下字段：\n21:    - 仓库名\n22:    - URL\n23:    - 主要语言（如可见）\n24:    - 热点原因/观察备注\n25:    - 来源说明\n26: 4. 复制 `reports/template.md` 作为新报告。\n27: 5. 按 `reports/YYYY-MM-DD-github-hot-repos.md` 命名保存。\n28: 6. 在报告头部明确说明是：\n29:    - 实际公开页面人工整理；或\n30:    - 样例/占位内容。\n31: \n32: ### 方案 B：半自动整理\n33: \n34: 1. 运行 `scripts/fetch_trending_no_token.py`，抓取公开页面候选列表。\n35: 2. 检查脚本输出是否为空、是否报错、是否出现解析异常。\n36: 3. 人工复核候选仓库信息后，再写入报告。\n37: 4. 若脚本失败，不要伪造自动采集结果，直接切回方案 A。\n38: \n39: 推荐命令：\n40: \n41: ```powershell\n42: python .\\scripts\\fetch_trending_no_token.py `\n43:   --since daily `\n44:   --limit 10 `\n45:   --json-out .\\state\\candidates\\daily-latest.json `\n46:   --md-out .\\state\\candidates\\daily-latest.md `\n47:   --log-file .\\state\\logs\\trending-fetch.log\n48: ```\n49: \n50: 补充说明：\n51: \n52: - 成功后会得到候选 JSON / Markdown，供人工复核。\n53: - 失败时脚本会输出人工兜底提示，不会伪造结果。\n54: - 退出码 `2` 表示网络或访问失败，`3` 表示解析失败或页面结构变化。\n55: \n56: ## 4. 建议的定期运行方式\n57: \n58: 当前版本不要求实际注册计划任务，但建议使用以下思路：\n59: \n60: ### Windows Task Scheduler\n61: \n62: - 建议频率：每日一次或每周一至周五一次。\n63: - 任务动作：\n64:   - 打开 PowerShell；\n65:   - 执行 `scripts/fetch_trending_no_token.py`；\n66:   - 由人工复核后生成 Markdown 报告。\n67: - 建议将标准输出/错误输出重定向到本地日志文件，便于排查。\n68: \n69: ### cron / 类 Unix 调度\n70: \n71: - 使用 `cron` 定时执行轻量脚本或提醒脚本。\n72: - 仍建议保留人工复核环节，避免页面结构变化导致静默错误。\n73: \n74: 更完整的调度步骤、失败处理和日志建议见 [`schedule-plan.md`](./schedule-plan.md)。\n75: \n76: ## 5. GitHub Trending 与公开来源的限制\n77: \n78: - GitHub Trending 页面并非稳定 API，页面结构可能变化。\n79: - 页面数据可能因地区、时间、缓存或实验策略而波动。\n80: - 无认证来源可能存在限流、访问失败、Cloudflare/反爬限制或短时不可达。\n81: - 若使用第三方公开聚合源，应在报告中说明其并非 GitHub 官方结构化 API。\n82: \n83: ## 6. 明确禁止事项\n84: \n85: - 不使用 GitHub token。\n86: - 不使用任何密钥、Cookie、登录态。\n87: - 不调用依赖私有凭据的接口。\n88: - 不把人工占位内容伪装成已验证实时抓取结果。\n89: \n90: ## 7. 失败、空结果、网络受限时的处理\n91: \n92: ### 网络失败\n93: \n94: - 在报告或运行记录中注明：无法访问公开来源。\n95: - 检查 `state/logs/trending-fetch.log` 与标准错误输出。\n96: - 如仍需交付，可生成“失败说明型报告”或人工占位报告。\n97: - 不要补写未经验证的数据。\n98: \n99: ### 空结果\n100: \n101: - 先判断是页面本身为空、脚本解析失败，还是来源结构变化。\n102: - 在报告中注明“空结果待复核”并保留错误现象。\n103: \n104: ### 页面结构变化\n105: \n106: - 记录失败原因。\n107: - 临时切换为人工整理模式。\n108: - 保留脚本错误输出与日志。\n109: - 后续再更新脚本或提取规则。\n110: \n111: ## 8. 产出要求\n112: \n113: - 报告必须存放于 `reports/`。\n114: - 命名遵循 `YYYY-MM-DD-github-hot-repos.md`。\n115: - 每份报告必须标注来源、采集方式和可信度说明。\n116: - 样例报告必须标明“样例”或“人工整理占位”，避免误导。\n117: \n118: ## 9. 后续可扩展方向\n119: \n120: - 增加语言/主题分类。\n121: - 对比相邻日期报告，生成新增/回归热点摘要。\n122: - 维护轻量状态索引，记录最近一次成功产出时间。\n\n(End of file - total 122 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# GitHub 热点仓库长期摘取整理报告 Runbook\n\n## 1. 目的\n\n本 runbook 用于指导后续 agent 或人工在**不使用 GitHub token、密钥、登录态**的前提下，持续产出 GitHub 热点仓库 Markdown 报告。\n\n## 2. 运行前提\n\n- 目标目录：`D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report`\n- 数据来源必须是公开、无需认证的页面或接口。\n- 不依赖外部服务部署。\n- 如无法联网，可退回人工占位/样例维护，但必须如实标注。\n\n## 3. 手动运行步骤\n\n### 方案 A：纯人工整理\n\n1. 打开 GitHub Trending 页面或其他公开热点来源。\n2. 记录本期观察日期、来源、时间范围（如 daily / weekly）。\n3. 选取若干热点仓库，整理以下字段：","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report\\runbook.md","time":{"start":1777267168860,"end":1777267168877}},"id":"prt_dcd60d657001EqBbS171xAxU8W","sessionID":"ses_2329f5659ffeTumX9K8lxuV4OV","messageID":"msg_dcd60c38d001cinoP7c4Acu5kp"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777267168883,"sessionID":"ses_2329f5659ffeTumX9K8lxuV4OV","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_5X8jQvKkP33yvgD8MbO9oGob","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report\\schedule-plan.md","limit":2000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report\\schedule-plan.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # GitHub 热点仓库定期调度方案\n2: \n3: ## 1. 目标\n4: \n5: 本方案用于在**不使用 GitHub token、密钥、Cookie、登录态**的前提下，定期运行轻量抓取脚本并保留人工复核环节。\n6: \n7: ## 2. 推荐频率\n8: \n9: - 默认建议：**每个工作日 09:00 本地时间执行一次**。\n10: - 如果维护成本更敏感，可退化为：**每周一、周三、周五执行一次**。\n11: - 不建议高频抓取（如每小时），避免无意义请求和页面限流风险。\n12: \n13: ## 3. 调度步骤\n14: \n15: ### 步骤 1：执行轻量脚本\n16: \n17: 在项目根目录运行：\n18: \n19: ```powershell\n20: python .\\scripts\\fetch_trending_no_token.py `\n21:   --since daily `\n22:   --limit 15 `\n23:   --json-out .\\state\\candidates\\daily-latest.json `\n24:   --md-out .\\state\\candidates\\daily-latest.md `\n25:   --log-file .\\state\\logs\\trending-fetch.log\n26: ```\n27: \n28: ### 步骤 2：检查命令退出状态\n29: \n30: - `0`：抓取和解析成功，进入人工复核。\n31: - `2`：网络访问失败（如超时、限流、无法访问）。\n32: - `3`：页面结构变化或解析失败。\n33: \n34: ### 步骤 3：人工复核\n35: \n36: 人工打开：\n37: \n38: - `state/candidates/daily-latest.json`\n39: - `state/candidates/daily-latest.md`\n40: - GitHub Trending 原始页面\n41: \n42: 确认候选仓库、语言、描述是否仍然合理后，再把结论写入 `reports/YYYY-MM-DD-github-hot-repos.md`。\n43: \n44: ## 4. 失败处理\n45: \n46: ### 网络失败 / GitHub 页面不可访问\n47: \n48: - 查看 `state/logs/trending-fetch.log`。\n49: - 在当期报告中写明：本次未能访问公开页面。\n50: - 如必须交付，退回 `runbook.md` 的“纯人工整理”流程。\n51: \n52: ### 解析失败 / 页面结构变化\n53: \n54: - 保留日志与标准错误输出。\n55: - 不要伪造脚本已成功抓取。\n56: - 在报告中标注“脚本失败，已切换人工整理”。\n57: - 后续再更新脚本解析逻辑。\n58: \n59: ### 输出为空\n60: \n61: - 先确认是否网络失败或 GitHub 页面结构变化。\n62: - 若原因不明，按解析失败处理并人工复核页面。\n63: \n64: ## 5. 日志位置\n65: \n66: - 建议日志目录：`state/logs/`\n67: - 建议抓取日志：`state/logs/trending-fetch.log`\n68: - 如使用外部调度器，可追加保存：\n69:   - 标准输出到 `state/logs/trending-fetch.stdout.log`\n70:   - 标准错误到 `state/logs/trending-fetch.stderr.log`\n71: \n72: ## 6. Windows Task Scheduler / cron 建议\n73: \n74: 本项目**当前只提供方案，不直接注册长期系统任务**。\n75: \n76: ### Windows Task Scheduler 建议动作\n77: \n78: ```powershell\n79: powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command \"Set-Location 'D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report'; python .\\scripts\\fetch_trending_no_token.py --since daily --limit 15 --json-out .\\state\\candidates\\daily-latest.json --md-out .\\state\\candidates\\daily-latest.md --log-file .\\state\\logs\\trending-fetch.log\"\n80: ```\n81: \n82: ### cron 建议动作\n83: \n84: ```bash\n85: cd /path/to/github-hot-repos-report && python3 ./scripts/fetch_trending_no_token.py --since daily --limit 15 --json-out ./state/candidates/daily-latest.json --md-out ./state/candidates/daily-latest.md --log-file ./state/logs/trending-fetch.log\n86: ```\n87: \n88: ## 7. 人工兜底要求\n89: \n90: - 脚本输出只能作为候选数据，不能直接视为最终热点报告。\n91: - 每次正式产出前都要人工抽查原页面。\n92: - 如果脚本失败，必须明确标注为人工整理或失败说明型报告。\n93: - 不允许因调度失败而伪造“自动采集成功”。\n\n(End of file - total 93 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# GitHub 热点仓库定期调度方案\n\n## 1. 目标\n\n本方案用于在**不使用 GitHub token、密钥、Cookie、登录态**的前提下，定期运行轻量抓取脚本并保留人工复核环节。\n\n## 2. 推荐频率\n\n- 默认建议：**每个工作日 09:00 本地时间执行一次**。\n- 如果维护成本更敏感，可退化为：**每周一、周三、周五执行一次**。\n- 不建议高频抓取（如每小时），避免无意义请求和页面限流风险。\n\n## 3. 调度步骤\n\n### 步骤 1：执行轻量脚本\n\n在项目根目录运行：\n\n```powershell\npython .\\scripts\\fetch_trending_no_token.py `","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report\\schedule-plan.md","time":{"start":1777267168854,"end":1777267168883}},"id":"prt_dcd60d6520020gic8ajrxPTixo","sessionID":"ses_2329f5659ffeTumX9K8lxuV4OV","messageID":"msg_dcd60c38d001cinoP7c4Acu5kp"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777267168889,"sessionID":"ses_2329f5659ffeTumX9K8lxuV4OV","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_1FK7EpyhV795wwxUYzpGGCcp","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report\\scripts\\fetch_trending_no_token.py","limit":2000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report\\scripts\\fetch_trending_no_token.py</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: #!/usr/bin/env python3\n2: \"\"\"Fetch public GitHub Trending candidates without authentication.\n3: \n4: This script intentionally uses only Python standard library modules and public\n5: GitHub Trending pages. It is a lightweight helper that generates candidate\n6: JSON/Markdown output for later human review.\n7: \"\"\"\n8: \n9: from __future__ import annotations\n10: \n11: import argparse\n12: import datetime as dt\n13: import html\n14: import json\n15: import pathlib\n16: import re\n17: import sys\n18: import urllib.error\n19: import urllib.parse\n20: import urllib.request\n21: \n22: \n23: SCRIPT_DIR = pathlib.Path(__file__).resolve().parent\n24: PROJECT_ROOT = SCRIPT_DIR.parent\n25: DEFAULT_USER_AGENT = (\n26:     \"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) \"\n27:     \"AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) \"\n28:     \"Chrome/124.0 Safari/537.36\"\n29: )\n30: \n31: \n32: def build_url(since: str, language: str | None, spoken_language: str | None) -> str:\n33:     params: dict[str, str] = {\"since\": since}\n34:     if spoken_language:\n35:         params[\"spoken_language_code\"] = spoken_language\n36: \n37:     base = \"https://github.com/trending\"\n38:     if language:\n39:         base = f\"{base}/{urllib.parse.quote(language)}\"\n40:     return f\"{base}?{urllib.parse.urlencode(params)}\"\n41: \n42: \n43: def fetch_html(url: str, timeout: int) -> str:\n44:     request = urllib.request.Request(\n45:         url,\n46:         headers={\n47:             \"User-Agent\": DEFAULT_USER_AGENT,\n48:             \"Accept\": \"text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8\",\n49:             \"Accept-Language\": \"en-US,en;q=0.9\",\n50:         },\n51:     )\n52:     with urllib.request.urlopen(request, timeout=timeout) as response:\n53:         charset = response.headers.get_content_charset() or \"utf-8\"\n54:         return response.read().decode(charset, errors=\"replace\")\n55: \n56: \n57: def _clean_text(raw: str | None) -> str | None:\n58:     if raw is None:\n59:         return None\n60:     text = html.unescape(raw)\n61:     text = re.sub(r\"<[^>]+>\", \" \", text)\n62:     text = text.replace(\"\\r\", \" \").replace(\"\\n\", \" \")\n63:     text = re.sub(r\"\\s+\", \" \", text).strip()\n64:     return text or None\n65: \n66: \n67: def parse_trending_page(page_html: str, source_url: str, limit: int) -> list[dict[str, str | None]]:\n68:     articles = re.findall(\n69:         r\"<article\\b[^>]*class=\\\"[^\\\"]*Box-row[^\\\"]*\\\"[^>]*>(.*?)</article>\",\n70:         page_html,\n71:         flags=re.IGNORECASE | re.DOTALL,\n72:     )\n73: \n74:     results: list[dict[str, str | None]] = []\n75:     for block in articles:\n76:         repo_match = re.search(\n77:             r\"<h2[^>]*>.*?<a[^>]*href=\\\"/([^\\\"]+)\\\"\",\n78:             block,\n79:             flags=re.IGNORECASE | re.DOTALL,\n80:         )\n81:         if not repo_match:\n82:             continue\n83: \n84:         repo_name = repo_match.group(1).strip().strip(\"/\")\n85:         url = f\"https://github.com/{repo_name}\"\n86: \n87:         desc_match = re.search(r\"<p[^>]*>(.*?)</p>\", block, flags=re.IGNORECASE | re.DOTALL)\n88:         lang_match = re.search(\n89:             r\"itemprop=\\\"programmingLanguage\\\"[^>]*>(.*?)</span>\",\n90:             block,\n91:             flags=re.IGNORECASE | re.DOTALL,\n92:         )\n93:         stars_match = re.search(\n94:             r\"href=\\\"/[^\\\"]+/stargazers\\\"[^>]*>\\s*([^<]+?)\\s*</a>\",\n95:             block,\n96:             flags=re.IGNORECASE | re.DOTALL,\n97:         )\n98:         today_match = re.search(\n99:             r\"<span[^>]*>\\s*([^<]*stars today[^<]*)\\s*</span>\",\n100:             block,\n101:             flags=re.IGNORECASE | re.DOTALL,\n102:         )\n103: \n104:         results.append(\n105:             {\n106:                 \"repo\": repo_name,\n107:                 \"url\": url,\n108:                 \"description\": _clean_text(desc_match.group(1) if desc_match else None),\n109:                 \"language\": _clean_text(lang_match.group(1) if lang_match else None),\n110:                 \"stars\": _clean_text(stars_match.group(1) if stars_match else None),\n111:                 \"stars_today\": _clean_text(today_match.group(1) if today_match else None),\n112:                 \"source\": source_url,\n113:             }\n114:         )\n115: \n116:         if len(results) >= limit:\n117:             break\n118: \n119:     return results\n120: \n121: \n122: def to_markdown(items: list[dict[str, str | None]], source_url: str, since: str) -> str:\n123:     today = dt.date.today().isoformat()\n124:     lines = [\n125:         \"# GitHub Trending 候选列表\",\n126:         \"\",\n127:         f\"- 生成日期：{today}\",\n128:         f\"- 来源：{source_url}\",\n129:         f\"- 范围：{since}\",\n130:         \"- 采集方式：无 token 公开页面抓取（待人工复核）\",\n131:         \"\",\n132:         \"## 候选仓库\",\n133:         \"\",\n134:     ]\n135: \n136:     for index, item in enumerate(items, start=1):\n137:         lines.extend(\n138:             [\n139:                 f\"### {index}. {item['repo']}\",\n140:                 \"\",\n141:                 f\"- URL：{item['url']}\",\n142:                 f\"- 主要语言：{item.get('language') or '未识别'}\",\n143:                 f\"- Stars：{item.get('stars') or '未识别'}\",\n144:                 f\"- 当日增量：{item.get('stars_today') or '未识别'}\",\n145:                 f\"- 描述：{item.get('description') or '无'}\",\n146:                 f\"- 备注：需人工复核页面内容后再写入正式报告。\",\n147:                 \"\",\n148:             ]\n149:         )\n150: \n151:     return \"\\n\".join(lines)\n152: \n153: \n154: def ensure_parent(path: pathlib.Path) -> None:\n155:     path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n156: \n157: \n158: def write_log(log_path: pathlib.Path, status: str, message: str) -> None:\n159:     ensure_parent(log_path)\n160:     timestamp = dt.datetime.now().isoformat(timespec=\"seconds\")\n161:     with log_path.open(\"a\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as fh:\n162:         fh.write(f\"[{timestamp}] {status}: {message}\\n\")\n163: \n164: \n165: def build_manual_fallback_message(url: str) -> str:\n166:     return (\n167:         \"未能稳定解析 GitHub Trending 公开页面。\\n\"\n168:         f\"请人工打开：{url}\\n\"\n169:         \"按 reports/template.md 手工整理候选仓库，并在正式报告中标明：\\n\"\n170:         \"- 本次为人工整理或脚本失败后人工兜底；\\n\"\n171:         \"- 未使用 token、Cookie、登录态；\\n\"\n172:         \"- 如页面结构变化，请在 runbook 中记录异常现象。\"\n173:     )\n174: \n175: \n176: def parse_args(argv: list[str]) -> argparse.Namespace:\n177:     parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(\n178:         description=\"Fetch GitHub Trending candidates without token or login.\",\n179:     )\n180:     parser.add_argument(\"--since\", choices=[\"daily\", \"weekly\", \"monthly\"], default=\"daily\")\n181:     parser.add_argument(\"--language\", help=\"Optional GitHub Trending language path segment.\")\n182:     parser.add_argument(\n183:         \"--spoken-language\",\n184:         help=\"Optional spoken_language_code query value, for example en or zh.\",\n185:     )\n186:     parser.add_argument(\"--limit\", type=int, default=10, help=\"Max repos to keep in output.\")\n187:     parser.add_argument(\"--timeout\", type=int, default=20, help=\"Network timeout in seconds.\")\n188:     parser.add_argument(\"--json-out\", help=\"Optional path to write JSON candidate output.\")\n189:     parser.add_argument(\"--md-out\", help=\"Optional path to write Markdown candidate output.\")\n190:     parser.add_argument(\n191:         \"--log-file\",\n192:         help=\"Optional append-only log path. Suggested: state/logs/trending-fetch.log\",\n193:     )\n194:     parser.add_argument(\n195:         \"--print-json\",\n196:         action=\"store_true\",\n197:         help=\"Print JSON candidates to stdout after a successful fetch.\",\n198:     )\n199:     return parser.parse_args(argv)\n200: \n201: \n202: def main(argv: list[str]) -> int:\n203:     args = parse_args(argv)\n204:     source_url = build_url(args.since, args.language, args.spoken_language)\n205: \n206:     try:\n207:         page_html = fetch_html(source_url, timeout=args.timeout)\n208:         items = parse_trending_page(page_html, source_url=source_url, limit=args.limit)\n209:         if not items:\n210:             raise RuntimeError(build_manual_fallback_message(source_url))\n211:     except urllib.error.HTTPError as exc:\n212:         message = (\n213:             f\"访问 GitHub Trending 失败，HTTP {exc.code}。\\n\"\n214:             f\"目标地址：{source_url}\\n\"\n215:             f\"{build_manual_fallback_message(source_url)}\"\n216:         )\n217:         if args.log_file:\n218:             write_log(pathlib.Path(args.log_file), \"ERROR\", f\"HTTP {exc.code} for {source_url}\")\n219:         print(message, file=sys.stderr)\n220:         return 2\n221:     except urllib.error.URLError as exc:\n222:         message = (\n223:             f\"访问 GitHub Trending 失败：{exc.reason}\\n\"\n224:             f\"目标地址：{source_url}\\n\"\n225:             f\"{build_manual_fallback_message(source_url)}\"\n226:         )\n227:         if args.log_file:\n228:             write_log(pathlib.Path(args.log_file), \"ERROR\", f\"URL error for {source_url}: {exc.reason}\")\n229:         print(message, file=sys.stderr)\n230:         return 2\n231:     except Exception as exc:\n232:         if args.log_file:\n233:             write_log(pathlib.Path(args.log_file), \"ERROR\", f\"Parse/runtime failure for {source_url}: {exc}\")\n234:         print(str(exc), file=sys.stderr)\n235:         return 3\n236: \n237:     payload = {\n238:         \"generated_at\": dt.datetime.now().isoformat(timespec=\"seconds\"),\n239:         \"source\": source_url,\n240:         \"since\": args.since,\n241:         \"language\": args.language,\n242:         \"spoken_language\": args.spoken_language,\n243:         \"count\": len(items),\n244:         \"items\": items,\n245:         \"note\": \"Candidates only. Human review required before final report.\",\n246:     }\n247: \n248:     if args.json_out:\n249:         json_path = pathlib.Path(args.json_out)\n250:         ensure_parent(json_path)\n251:         json_path.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n252: \n253:     if args.md_out:\n254:         md_path = pathlib.Path(args.md_out)\n255:         ensure_parent(md_path)\n256:         md_path.write_text(to_markdown(items, source_url=source_url, since=args.since), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n257: \n258:     if args.log_file:\n259:         write_log(pathlib.Path(args.log_file), \"OK\", f\"Fetched {len(items)} repos from {source_url}\")\n260: \n261:     if args.print_json or (not args.json_out and not args.md_out):\n262:         print(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n263:     else:\n264:         summary = f\"Fetched {len(items)} repos from {source_url}\"\n265:         print(summary)\n266: \n267:     return 0\n268: \n269: \n270: if __name__ == \"__main__\":\n271:     raise SystemExit(main(sys.argv[1:]))\n\n(End of file - total 271 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Fetch public GitHub Trending candidates without authentication.\n\nThis script intentionally uses only Python standard library modules and public\nGitHub Trending pages. It is a lightweight helper that generates candidate\nJSON/Markdown output for later human review.\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport datetime as dt\nimport html\nimport json\nimport pathlib\nimport re\nimport sys\nimport urllib.error\nimport urllib.parse\nimport urllib.request","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\projects\\github-hot-repos-report\\scripts\\fetch_trending_no_token.py","time":{"start":1777267168850,"end":1777267168888}},"id":"prt_dcd60d64f001Z0GMokSguV6MYw","sessionID":"ses_2329f5659ffeTumX9K8lxuV4OV","messageID":"msg_dcd60c38d001cinoP7c4Acu5kp"}}
